From 83ed2d25149ae05503a00fefed07cf4ac48cac53 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Bernhard=20Rosenkr=C3=A4nzer?= <bero@lindev.ch>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 19:10:43 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 11/13] Add full tcmalloc as LD_PRELOAD DSO
 (--with-malloc-preload=tcmalloc)

Ship gperftools libtcmalloc (sampling + heap profiler, not
tcmalloc_minimal) as libglibc_malloc_tcmalloc.so.  Compile with the
system C++ toolchain headers to avoid glibc include/ clashes, and omit
libunwind so preload TLS setup does not recurse into malloc under the
new ld.so.  Preload-only by design (libstdc++).
