new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..ff0d7f6dfc
--- /dev/null
+++ b/malloc/tcmalloc/README-GLIBC.md
@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+In-tree copy of gperftools **libtcmalloc** (full, not `tcmalloc_minimal`)
+for LD_PRELOAD use: allocation sampling and the heap profiler are enabled.
+The CPU profiler lives in upstream `libtcmalloc_and_profiler` and is not
+linked here.
+
+Built as `libglibc_malloc_tcmalloc.so` via
+`--with-malloc-preload=tcmalloc`.  Not embeddable in `libc.so` (C++ /
+libstdc++ dependency); preload-only is intentional.
