+ * profiled.)
+ *
+ * Use pprof to view the resulting profile output.
+ *    % pprof <path_to_executable> <profile_file_name>
+ *    % pprof --gv  <path_to_executable> <profile_file_name>
+ *
+ * These functions are thread-safe.
+ */
